Mushrooms of the PNW

Tue, September 15, 6:00 pm - 8:00 pm

  • « To Go: The Greek Isles
  • To Go: Farm Harvest Supper »

There are two options for this class! You can shop for your own ingredients or we are happy to pre-measure ingredients and assemble them into a 4-serving kit for you to pick up. If you would like to purchase ingredients from us, please add the class option that includes an ingredients kit to your shopping cart. Ingredients Kits are available for purchase up to 6 days before class, and can be picked up in our garden between 10am-6pm the day before class. 

To get a jump start on class, you can preview the ingredients and equipment needed by following this link. One week before class we will send out a detailed shopping list, and two days before class we will email you a detailed recipe packet and Zoom link. All classes are listed in Pacific Daylight Time.
